---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section id="faq" class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Got questions...? We have all the answers!</h2>
            <div class="faq-container">
              <details>
                <summary>What is OJUBABES Matchmaking?</summary>
                <p>OJUBABES is a personalized matchmaking service designed to help you find a serious and meaningful relationship. We focus on detailed profiles and verified members to ensure a high-quality experience.</p>
              </details>
              <details>
                <summary>Is my data secure?</summary>
                <p>Absolutely. We prioritize your privacy and use secure systems to protect your information. Please read our Privacy Policy for more details.</p>
              </details>
              <details>
                <summary>How does the matching process work?</summary>
                <p>Our algorithm considers your profile, preferences, and values to suggest compatible matches. We believe in quality over quantity.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="section">
    <div class="container footer-container">
        <div class="footer-column">
            <h3>OJUBABES Matchmaking</h3>
            <p>Your journey to finding true love starts here. We are committed to helping you find your perfect match.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-column">
            <h3>Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/about">About Us</a>
                <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
                <a href="#">Terms & Conditions</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-column">
            <h3>Connect With Us</h3>
            <div class="social-icons">
              <a href="#" class="social-icon"><img src="/instagram.jpeg" alt="Instagram"></a>
              <a href="#" class="social-icon"><img src="/tiktok.png" alt="TikTok"></a>
              <a href="#" class="social-icon"><img src="/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
              <a href="#" class="social-icon"><img src="/x.png" alt="X"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container copyright">
        <p>&copy; 2025 OJUBABES Matchmaking. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
</footer>
</Layout>
